com.github.keenon.lense.lense

Class LenseWithRetraining

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.keenon.lense.lense.LenseWithRetraining

  • public class LenseWithRetraining
extends Object
    Created by keenon on 10/7/15. Handles running Lense, and a thread that learns new weights from Lense output whenever new classifications finish. This is pretty basic stuff, but it's a very common case for Lense use.
